episodes.title: Ties That Bind
episodes.description: Mary recruits Frankie and Trudy to find a missing teacher, but their investigation leads them to family secrets, Chinatown, and murder.

episodes.title: The Pilot
episodes.description: A day off turns into a day at the office for Frankie and Trudy when the infant son of a charismatic aviator is kidnapped during an air show.

episodes.title: Ghosts
episodes.description: The horrors of war haunt Frankie when an investigation into a soldier’s murder reunites her with a friend left traumatized by his tour of duty.

episodes.title: Anastasia
episodes.description: Frankie is hired to confirm the identity of a young woman claiming to be a Russian princess and protect her from those who want her dead.

episodes.title: Once Burnt Twice Spied
episodes.description: When Frankie gets a mysterious call from a British spy, Mary discovers how she and Trudy met, and how Drake Private Detectives was formed.

episodes.title: The Old Switcheroo
episodes.description: An old rival turns up selling antiquities, but Frankie's convinced it's all a scam. Can the team prove it before she takes the money and runs?

episodes.title: Last Dance
episodes.description: The team investigates a kidnapping gone wrong at the Palais Royale. They learn the victim is gravely ill and race to find him and save his life.

episodes.title: Radio Daze
episodes.description: Mary is acting in a radio drama, but when she realizes the play is a cover for a heist, she must find a way to warn Frankie.

episodes.title: Emancipation Day
episodes.description: When donations are taken from a colored girls' orphanage, civil rights hero Marcus Garvey hires the team to catch the thief and find the cash.

episodes.title: Dressed to Kill
episodes.description: When famed French designer Coco Chanel is the target of a brazen assassination attempt, Drake Private Detectives are hired to protect her.

episodes.title: Extra Innings
episodes.description: Frankie suspects sabotage when a baseball player dies mid-game. Her investigation puts her at odds with ruthless mobster Bessie Starkman.
